        "content": "<p>I have created a statement of the Monty Hall brain teaser and proved some parts, but I am still stick with most of the proofs. Could someone help me to advance a little bit?</p>\n<p>I mainly don't know how to reduce the created measure and calculate probabilities.</p>\n<p>The code is on this PR <a href=\"https://github.com/wvhulle/riddle-proofs/pull/1\">https://github.com/wvhulle/riddle-proofs/pull/1</a>.</p>",
